      <scopecontent id="aspace_26a47910f3c719ddef2087c0ebc845bd">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Collection of projects completed by graduate students in classes of the Yale School of Art Graphic Design Program. Items include projects produced for classes taught by Bradbury Thompson, Paul Rand, and Alvin Eisenman. Documentation includes projects themselves as well as a series of slides providing images of projects.</p>
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_b20b9516a76345a07ee5e899aebe8ebe">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Arranged in four series: Binding Design Projects; Book Design Projects; Type Design Projects; and Slides.</p>
      </arrangement>
